Package de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.pubsub.model.tree.utils

An utility package to iterate/chop a tree.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Iterable
    Interface to determine that an Object is iterable by an Iterator
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BFSIterator
    Concrete Iterator which uses the breadth first search (DFS) method to chop the PubSub-tree
    DFSIterator
    Concrete Iterator which uses the depth first search (DFS) method to chop the PubSub-tree
    Iterator
    This abstract Iterator implements the java.util.Iterator interface and may be extended to line-up several de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.pubsub.model.tree.utils.Iterable in a protected List (called list).

Package de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.pubsub.model.tree.utils Description

An utility package to iterate/chop a tree. Only Nodes which do implement the Iterable interface may be iterated
